snippet.textDisplay: I haattteeeee meatloaf i was a little bit of a picky eater but I loved fruits and veggies so it’s not like I only wanted sweets, but meatloaf was literally my nightmare dinner as a kid and that and pizza were the only foods that my mom would have to get me something else bc I refused to eat. I still to this day feel nauseous when I see meatloaf or smell it. I actually went to a family friends Christmas party this year and the main meal was meatloaf so I ate pickles, olives, and buffalo dip the whole day
